From 9e4522b3ae14ed29f3c383069da3344edbd17c06 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: PVM Playbook <pvm@local>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 15:20:46 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add PVM Firecracker Ansible playbook (no-KVM microVMs)

Adds an idempotent, role-based Ansible playbook that builds the entire
no-KVM PVM Firecracker stack from a bare Rocky/Alma/RHEL 10 host:
preflight (asserts x86_64 + RHEL + fsgsbase), packages, PVM-patched
Firecracker, PVM host kernel, PVM guest kernel, Ubuntu rootfs, GRUB +
reboot, and an end-to-end microVM smoke test.

Usage:
    cd pvm-firecracker-ansible
    # edit inventory.ini -> your host
    ansible-playbook playbook.yml
